{"tid":2067434,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連鎖童裝店放巨型民主女神像　老闆：盼教孩子民主自由","createTime":"2020-06-17T04:10:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-17T04:10:20.000Z","uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"64543e07758137924a114cdcbb344ebf80921e69","tid":2067434,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T04:10:20.000Z","msg":"一座 2 米高的香港民主女神像，昨晚（16 日）起落戶在荃灣愉景新城的童裝店 Chickeeduck。老闆周小龍今日親自到場監督擺設，更在店內放置有關民主的兒童圖書，期望童裝店可以成為小孩學習民主自由意識的地方。<br />\n<br />\n在設置香港民主女神像之前，周小龍稱做足手續，強調有知會這個新世界旗下的大商場，「發了電郵，只是附了照片以後就沒有回覆」 ，他評估，只是把一個藝術品放在自家店內，應當是沒問題。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/連鎖童裝店設民主女神像-老闆-昐教孩子民主自由/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E9%80%A3%E9%8E%96%E7%AB%A5%E8%A3%9D%E5%BA%97%E8%A8%AD%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E5%A5%B3%E7%A5%9E%E5%83%8F-%E8%80%81%E9%97%86-%E6%98%90%E6%95%99%E5%AD%A9%E5%AD%90%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%2F&d=3WJ6yD1ie6zkJWt%2B9GiXGz2djVMnfBKxsW1BXeekzK0%3D&h=6e11d2e3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E9%80%A3%E9%8E%96%E7%AB%A5%E8%A3%9D%E5%BA%97%E8%A8%AD%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E5%A5%B3%E7%A5%9E%E5%83%8F-%E8%80%81%E9%97%86-%E6%98%90%E6%95%99%E5%AD%A9%E5%AD%90%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%2F&h=77e8fa4b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/連鎖童裝店設民主女神像-老闆-昐教孩子民主自由/</a>"}]}